# Hello World React App Project Rules

This is an animated Hello World React application with the following structure:
- Main entry point: [src/index.js](mdc:src/index.js)
- Main component: [src/App.js](mdc:src/App.js) 
- Styling: [src/App.css](mdc:src/App.css) and [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css)
- Configuration: [package.json](mdc:package.json)

## Code Writing Policy
**CRITICAL**: Do not write any code unless explicitly requested by the user. This rule is mentioned in [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md).

## Project Context
- This is a demo React app that toggles between "Hello World" and "Bye World"
- Features complex CSS animations including spinning, sliding, and gradient effects
- Uses React hooks (useState) for state management
- Designed as an interactive showcase of React and CSS capabilities
